title: Top 101 free agents
itunes:title: Top 101 free agents
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – discuss all the latest news from around the NFL including the Jets cutting veteran center Nick Mangold, plus, a breakdown of all the players who have been given franchise tags so far. Then, the heroes release their annual list of the top 101 free agents.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
